de.wagnst.tpe.exercises.exercise2.master

Class Currencies

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.wagnst.tpe.exercises.exercise2.master.Currencies

  • public final class Currencies
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains defined objects of currency with its exchange rate to dollar, name, currency symbol and an information if it has a subunit

    This class could normally better be replaces with a enum, because it does not use the features of a class. It simply creates currencies with the help of the Currency class.

    Author:
    maxGross, wagnst
